S.FORM: matabesiu ku palamalan a lisin masumad tu ku demiad , , a malingatu tu silielip, kasililipan u puu' nu mihcan kaydaan, malingatu tu palespesan tu kudemiad,sienaw sienaw tu kudemiad. . u sakasaan katukuhan tu nanaytu ku sadingsing , 也就是秋天到了, yu kasu mamadan namakayni ku sayaway, , misupped tu kasuy ku paylumaluma'an, qsapi likeluh tu sienaw ami sangidu ilabu nu luma', , paka dihku tu labunu nuluma', u nanam tu nukawaw nu malukay. .

matabesio ko palamalan a lisin masomad to ko demiad , , a malingato to silielip, kasililipan o poo' no mihcan kaydaan, malingato to palespesan to kodemiad,sienaw sienaw to kodemiad. . o sakasaan katokohan to nanayto ko sadingsing , 也就是秋天到了, yo kaso mamadan namakayni ko sayaway, , misopped to kasoy ko paylomaloma'an, qsapi likeloh to sienaw ami sangido ilabo no loma', , paka dihko to labono noloma', o nanam to nokawaw no malokay. .
